    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract base for command buffers that collect and flush commands. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1CommandBuffer" kindref="compound">CommandBuffer</ref> defines the interface for deferred command execution. Commands are accumulated during the frame and flushed at defined commit points in the game loop. Concrete implementations (e.g., <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandBuffer" kindref="compound">TypedCommandBuffer</ref>) provide type-safe storage and routing.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandBuffer" kindref="compound">TypedCommandBuffer</ref> </para>
